Ext.data.JsonP['Problems_View']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Problems View</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083300\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Problems View</h1>\n    <p>This page gives an overview of how to use the Problems View to identify syntax errors.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083300_ProblemsView-Introduction\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Introduction</span></h2>\n    <p>While editing a file in one of our editors or after saving files, our index and validation process will parse the files for warnings and errors, which will be shown in the Problems View.    </p>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083300/RubySyntaxError.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083300/RubySyntaxError.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083300_ProblemsView-RelatedTopics\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Related Topics</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"childpages-macro \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Adding_custom_error_message_filters_to_the_Problems_View\">Adding custom error message filters to the Problems View</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Enabling_and_disabling_validation\">Enabling and disabling validation</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083300\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Problems View"});